name: THE FOUR SEASONS GREETING CARDS
description:
THE FOUR SEASONS (set of 4 cards) are beautifully represented through the four types of the TAN rabbit breed.

These are 5.5" x 4" printed cards from the artist's original designs. The inside is blank. 

Glossy finish.

Your cards will be packaged in a padded envelope. Cardboard will be placed inside with a note on the outside DO NOT BEND.
